Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:13.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Boli sme tak blízko! Nechali ste ich všetkých ujsť!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Vždy ste takí pomalí!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?! Ty sa nám vždy postavíš do cesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:23.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ticho! Ja vždy upratujem to, čo pokazíte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Skúste si moju prácu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:26.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:33.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa vrátite, chcem, aby ste boli niekým iným!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:35.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:36.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Byť niekým iným...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:38.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...úplne?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:40.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo tým myslel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:48.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:05.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Pod vysvieteným kopcom sme si vyznali počiatok lásky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.34,0:01:08.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Kvôli tebe a aj sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:19.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po tisícročiach osamelosti som sa stretla s tvojím uhrančivým pohľadom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:21.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem byť spojená!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to príjemný pocit vzrušenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:36.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to, ako keby sa táto sila zrodila z morskej peny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:42.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:45.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Tieto slzy dojatia, to rozhodne nie je žiadny sen,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:47.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}toto je útek za láskou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Všetko čo máme sú naše srdcia
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:53.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Naše nádeje sú v nekonečnej čiernej diere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:59.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem, aby sme boli spojení, a to naveky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:14.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(318,212)\fad(0,1000)}"Hra kostýmov duše."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:17.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáčte za čakanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si tak oblečený?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:24.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som Tsugumi Rosenmeier zo Severného Špeciálneho Obranného obvodu Gelman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teší ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neverím tomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:31.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun, si to ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je príliš... proste príliš.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Odporné.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.83,0:02:40.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako... Ako si mohol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:47.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nehovor to! Mohla... Mohla som vybuchnúť!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nieee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje melónové chleby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nieee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú moje!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zašiel si príliš ďaleko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:12.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aký to malo význam?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:19.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aby si sa niekým stala, tak musíš začať s výzorom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš... kostýmovú hru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:30.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno. Vždy som robil fotky, keď som bol v Neo-Ázii.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mám kostým pre každého.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre každého?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravili mi ich priatelia z Deavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:51.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôže byť vážny...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:56.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia a Reika, Pierre a Chloe, Apollo a Sirius
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:57.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,si vymenia oblečenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Začína cvičenie hrania!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:07.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Prečo musím byť Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:12.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo? Prečo sa musím obliecť ako barbar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:16.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ani to nie je pre mňa. Kto chce imitovať princa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Je to také zlé?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jasné! Strašne zlé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nápodobne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, áno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:29.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To znamená, že ste si v niečom podobný.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:31.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo musíš byť Apollo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to podľa základnej psychológie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:43.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď vycítiš svoje pocity u iného,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak to silno odmietneš.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Inými slovami, osobu, s ktorou má problémy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:54.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,je osoba podobná tomu, čo nechceš vidieť v sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovoríš, že Reika a ja sme podobné?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je... nešťastie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaša psychika a projekcia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:09.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,je jasná, Reika, Sirius a Chloe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale tamto a toto je iné.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:17.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, chápeš teóriu, ale zážitok je iný.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:23.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepoužívaj hlavu! Cíť to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:28.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, Chloe, vždy si tak ďaleko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Znamená to, že sme podobní?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sranduješ!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:37.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... otestujeme to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môj bože...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:56.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre, prečo ťa tak zaujímajú iné ženy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:01.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozeraj sa iba na mňa... dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba na mňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:05.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:13.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som vždy taká vážna, že iba Pierre sa ku mne priblíži...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, myslela si to vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, ako som povedala.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:23.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potlačovaná psychika a projekcia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítim vášeň!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:32.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat... buď milší na Silviu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:37.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je mi z teba zle! Neurážaj moju sestru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:42.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, brat! Znieš ako Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kruté...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:51.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To bolo presne ako ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si povedala?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Viac nešťastia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Také nešťastie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:17.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítim nebezpečenstvo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú moje!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preč!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dosť presvedčivé.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevyzerá to, že máme na výber.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:42.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:47.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat? Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde môže byť?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:53.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde by bol?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:56.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Také nešťastie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:59.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Súrodenci, rozdelený...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:05.12,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, tak nakoniec sme sa stretli, moja milovaná sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:12.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja milovaná sestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:18.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Br... Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:24.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat... tak tu si bol! Hľadala som ťa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:26.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, nehľadala!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Drž svoje ruky od môjho brata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si sama sebou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:39.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika! Išla si pre brata, ako ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Osoba, ktorú chceš, je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď, moja milovaná sestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prestaň!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:08.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia sa to snaží zakryť, ale zdá sa, že sa zaľúbila do Apolla,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,do reinkarnácie jej milovaného z minulého života.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomu neverím...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:20.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, Pierre, nesmieš popierať pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pravdu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Touché.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítim vášeň.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:32.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pochopil si to zle! Tak perfektne som to hral, bola taká zmätená!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:41.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, kvet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Taká krásna vôňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:49.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo ľudia tak vyhladnú?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:58.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto ti neprejde!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:06.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za pretiahnutú tvár?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je tu nič ako kostýmová hra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:15.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš hrať, ale neoklameš môj nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hnusné.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dosť dobré...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:48.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úbohé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rena, môžeš chodiť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžeš imitovať hlas a slová,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:56.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ale vo vnútri si stále, kto si bol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ! Od kedy ste...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Od začiatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale potom, kde je Rena?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:14.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Na ošetrovni, s anémiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:18.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, starec! Ktorá časť z nás je ten výzor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:28.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Raz žaba, vždy žaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žiadna žaba sa nesnaží byť žabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:47.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, už je neskoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:51.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,"Žiadna žaba sa nesnaží byť žabou."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kedy som zaostal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:12:01.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo ju dokáže chytiť a zjesť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjesť... toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:08.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hnusné!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:15.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo raz povedal, že ide zjesť korisť z lesov Deavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Loviť v lesoch Deavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nájde korisť podľa vône.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vône?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vône, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, kam ideš?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:33.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediný spôsob, ako sa úplne stať Apollom, je ísť na lov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslí to vážne...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:44.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bojím sa, že môžu imitovať vonkajšie pocity,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:49.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ale stále je priskoro, aby sa postarali o temnotu ich sŕdc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:53.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Deti vždy vyrastú skôr, než ich rodičia čakajú.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:13:01.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Skoro už vedia tajomstvo troch šípov.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:04.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale veliteľ, povedali ste, že v tejto dobe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:10.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,sa môžu zlomiť aj 3 šípy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa stanú jednou osobou, tak s tým musia bojovať...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:22.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3 šípy ukážu obrovskú podobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obrovskú podobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:53.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:08.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie... Nie... Otec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:12.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Otec! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:15.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo si to povedala?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, brat! Zhoríš!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nesmieš ísť!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:29.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To som... ja?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:43.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie! Nenechávaj ma samú!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:49.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra, takáto upravená izba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako sa mám stať človekom ako on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za pach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:17.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bože... Som ako Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:27.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Má Reika vždy toľko nešťastia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zašiel by si tak ďaleko, aby si sa stal Apollom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:51.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak ja sa stanem Reikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:55.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius, nenechám ťa trpieť samého...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten Apollo... tu loví?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvety...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:36.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Voňajú pekne...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítim, že niečo horí!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:42.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oheň...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko zhorelo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie... Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Také netaktné...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď von!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepáči sa mi to... Cítim niečo zlé...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:21.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vectory?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýtická beštia sa stala Vectormi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:28.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potvrdil som ich vysoko úrovňové kvantové vzory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:32.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sú to perfektné kópie od ich veľkosti až po energický znak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:34.96,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké odporné, že nás napodobňujú!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Neodpustiteľné!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Sol jednotkám Vector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:43.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Formácia S-L-M. Kódové meno: Nádherný tvar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:44.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čas ísť!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:51.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Úžasné! Hrajú aj bez kostýmov!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:56.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:06.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to na nič! Tretia úroveň citov zjednotenia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,nie je dostatočná!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:12.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tretia úroveň citov... duševná úroveň...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýtická beštia sa blíži!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:19.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri! Nepriateľ sa ide zjednotiť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:23.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nemôže byť! Ako sa môže nepriateľ zjednotiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:29.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Už viem! Nepriateľ kopíruje posledný Aquarion Gattai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Prečo sa nemôžeme zjednotiť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prečo je to tak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:48.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Raz žaba, vždy žaba. Raz jastrab, vždy jastrab.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Raz vlk, vždy vlk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:53.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ, čo to znamená?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:55.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Raz žaba, vždy žaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíte, aby sa stali niekým iným?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:07.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra! Stále nás kopírujú!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kopírujú...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kopírujú?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:16.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môžem kopírovať koho chcem, ale ja som ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:20.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Presne! Ja som ja! Čo sa s tým deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:23.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre povedané, Silvia. Naozaj si moja sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:26.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:30.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tretia úroveň citov je na úrovni zjednotenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:33.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Cítim Siriusovu a Silviinu auru v mojom tele!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Taká neuveriteľne vysoká.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:47.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to neskutočné. Mám pocit topenia a nadšenia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:55.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvládli to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je skutočnosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obrovská...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:12.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...sa zväčšuje!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrý bože!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aury kvantumu Solar Aquariona narastajú.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:21.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Berie hmotu z okolia a zväčšuje sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:25.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže to byť... Obria podoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:34.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3 šípy namierené rovnakým smerom, môžu byť zničené.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:40.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ak 3 šípy uznajú svoju existenciu navzájom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:44.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a pôjdu inymi smermi, tak sa vyvinú.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.69,0:20:50.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ak pôjdu inými smermi, nebude to na nič?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak pôjdu náhodne, tak áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:57.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ak sa 3 šípy stanú jedným zo všetkých,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:01.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,hlboko sa precítia a nájdu prepojenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:06.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,prepojenie medzi žabami, jastrabmi a vlkmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:12.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3 Vectory! Stroje Vector!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:16.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa 3 Vectory rozšíria z centra ich troch duší
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:20.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,v troch smeroch: Hore-dole, vľavo-vpravo a nebo-zem,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,3 šípy prekročia dimenzie
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:27.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,do troj dimenzionálneho rozmeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:32.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorím to všetkým, prekročte dimenzie a dajte život obriemu svetu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:41.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Podceňujú nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:45.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Obyčajná kópia nemôže skopírovať naše duše!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:47.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spravme to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Trans-dimenzionálny, nekonečný útok!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:53.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,89)}"Super 3D útok Mugen"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:25.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Stanú sa osobou, ktorú najviac nenávidia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:28.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,tak najdú svoje pravé ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:33.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to bolo, čo spojilo ich 3 šípy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.67,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som taká šťastná... všetci žijú...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.13,0:23:48.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kruh, kruh, hore, dole...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:49.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo to znamenalo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:52.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerome, to nie je nevyriešený kód.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:53.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to len grafit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:55.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Grafit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.18,0:23:57.68,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovy: "Darebáctvo bez zlého úmyslu"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:24:00.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(317,219)}"Darebáctvo bez zlého úmyslu"
